  "body": "Hi, \r\n\r\nrook uses ubuntu/debian based docker images , if you take a look at the cve report from clair (cve sacnner from coreos)\r\n\r\nthere are over 100 known unfixed CVEs\r\n\r\n[analysis-registry.xxx.net-rook-v0.7.1_thirdparty.0.html.txt](https://github.com/rook/rook/files/1842104/analysis-registry.xxx.net-rook-v0.7.1_thirdparty.0.html.txt)\r\n\r\nthe most CVEs are unfixed in Debian/Ubuntu\r\n\r\nIf you take a look at centos e.g there are 0 unfixed CVEs in the centos:7 image\r\n\r\n\r\nSwitching to centos:7 would be a big security improvment\r\n\r\n\r\n ",
